'''国际抗癫痫联盟'''（{{lang-en|'''International League Against Epilepsy'''}}，{{lang|en|'''ILAE'''}}）是一个成立于1909年的医师及其他卫生工作者的协会。国际抗癫痫联盟的目标有：推动癫痫知识的进步和传播，推动相关的研究、教育和培训，（特别是通过预防、诊断、治疗）改善对癫痫病人的护理服务。<ref>{{cite web|title=ILAE Goals, Mission, and Strategy|url=http://www.ilae.org/Visitors/About_ILAE/mission.cfm|publisher=International League Against Epilepsy|accessdate=2015-02-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405085943/http://www.ilae.org/Visitors/About_ILAE/mission.cfm|archivedate=2015-04-05}}</ref>

国际抗癫痫联盟經常與[[国际癫痫署|国际癫痫署]]合作，促进大众对癫痫病的理解认识。<ref>{{cite web|title=Epilepsy.org|url=http://www.epilepsy.org/|accessdate=14 May 2014|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215103545/http://www.epilepsy.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>国际癫痫署、国际抗癫痫联盟与[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]在1997年发起了“全球抗癫痫运动”（Global Campaign Against Epilepsy），以促进各国努力解决癫痫病人的问题<ref>{{cite book|last=al.]|first=Jerome Engel ... [et|title=Epilepsy global issues for the practicing neurologist|year=2005|publisher=Demos Medical Pub.|location=New York, N.Y.|isbn=9781934559123|page=138|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=hFk4kt1o3mwC&pg=PT138|access-date=2015-02-15|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215103410/http://books.google.ca/books?id=hFk4kt1o3mwC&pg=PT138|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Prasher|first=edited by Vee P.|title=Epilepsy and intellectual disabilities|year=2008|publisher=Springer|location=New York|isbn=9781848002593|page=212|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=Oze51wrSUGEC&pg=PA212|author2=Kerr, Mike P.|access-date=2015-02-15|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215105737/http://books.google.ca/books?id=Oze51wrSUGEC&pg=PA212|dead-url=no}}</ref>

